{"id":317904,"type":2,"name":"民族痛史","summary":"《民族痛史》是一部反帝题材影片，影片描写鸦片战争后，帝国主义列强侵略中国，当时的统治者都实行卖国投降政策，签订了一个个不平等条约，使中国沦为帝国主义的殖民地的，最终给中华民族带来灾难和痛苦的“民族痛史”。\r\n\r\n影片于1934年获国民党政府内政部、教育部奖状。这是中国第一部在国内获奖的美术片。\r\n\r\n简介来自http://www.shtong.gov.cn/dfz_web/DFZ/Info?idnode=63937&tableName=userobject1a&id=11579","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>民族痛史</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万超尘</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万涤寰</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\">万超尘</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\">万涤寰</a>、<a href=\"/person/40054\">王乾白</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\">万超尘</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\">万涤寰</a></li><li><span>录音: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\">万涤寰</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\">万超尘</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1936年</li><li><span>製作: </span>明星影業公司</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"中国","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":986024,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986024","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":33269,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b0/94/33269_prsn_p0686.jpg","name":"万嘉坤","desc":"导演"},{"id":15676,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a0/fe/15676_prsn_6A9N0.jpg","name":"万嘉淇","desc":"导演"},{"id":15675,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/98/37/15675_prsn_792Dd.jpg","name":"万嘉综","desc":"导演"},{"id":22173,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2d/cb/22173_prsn_6lI6m.jpg","name":"万嘉结","desc":"导演"},{"id":40054,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/28/20/40054_prsn_FG2Fh.jpg","name":"王乾白","desc":"脚本"}]}